  "title": "Locum Pharmacy Technician (Office Hours, North-East ) – Up to $3.5K #HTJ",
  "description": "<p><strong>Mon to Fri (office hours)</strong><br /><strong>Alternate Saturday</strong></p><p><strong>Salary: $20 per hour</strong></p><p><strong>*6 months contract renewable</strong></p><p><u>Job Description:</u></p><p><p>Process prescriptions and dispense medications </p></p><p><p>Support medication delivery and remote collection services </p></p><p><p>Provide tele-dispensing services when required</p></p><p>Assist with video consultations and medication reconciliation<br /></p><p><u>Requirements:</u></p><ul><li>GCE ‘O’ Level with a Certificate in Pharmacy Technician Course (under MOH, PSS or its equivalent) or Diploma in Pharmaceutical Science</li><li>Pharmacy technician experience will be an advantage</li></ul><p>Interested candidates, please send your resume to <em><strong>jalenetan@recruitexpress.com.sg</strong></em></p><p><br />Jalene Tan<br />Outsourced Team<br />Recruit Express Pte Ltd, EA License No.: 99C4599</p>",
